h3. Message

Camel supports the [Message|http://www.enterpriseintegrationpatterns.com/Message.html] from the [EIP patterns|Enterprise Integration Patterns] using the [Message|http://camel.apache.org/maven/current/camel-core/apidocs/org/apache/camel/Message.html] interface. 

!http://www.enterpriseintegrationpatterns.com/img/MessageSolution.gif!

To support various message [exchange patterns|Exchange Pattern] like one way [Event Message] and [Request Reply] messages Camel uses an [Exchange] interface which has a *pattern* property which can be set to *InOnly* for an [Event Message] which has a single inbound Message, or *InOut* for a [Request Reply] where there is an inbound and outbound message.
 
